---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
const { cta_url } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="The Book of Wisdom PDF offers profound insights from the esoteric realm, aiding in the evolution of your mind, body, and soul.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="The Book of Wisdom, esoteric knowledge, occult information, personal growth, spiritual enlightenment, PDF, digital product, hidden insights, 119 pages">
    <meta property="og:title" content="The Book of Wisdom">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Uncover hidden truths and deep esoteric insights with the Book of Wisdom PDF. A treasury of wisdom to facilitate the evolution of your mind, body, and soul.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/BookOfWisdom.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content={cta_url}>
    <meta property="og:type" content="book">
    <title>The Book of Wisdom</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href={cta_url}>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 mb-8 mt-12 sm:mt-12 sm:mb-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-32 md:mb-20 xl:mt-23 xl:mb-24">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="mb-12 md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
          <h1
            class="mt-1 text-5xl tracking-tight leading-16 font-extrabold sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl uppercase"
          ><span class="underline">The Book of Wisdom</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <b>The Book of Wisdom</b> PDF, featured in the online videos you've viewed, offers a deep treasury of esoteric knowledge. Beyond surface-level truths, this book reveals profound hidden insights to aid you in understanding the connections between yourself and the universe.</p>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            Packed with 119 pages of easily digestible wisdom, this PDF is designed to awaken your mind, body, and soul. It offers an abundance of occult information, guiding you through a revival of enlightenment. The truths within will facilitate your personal and spiritual evolution.</p>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <b>Note:</b> This is a digital product (PDF), and you will receive an email with download instructions. You can also access the PDF via the Course Portal. Digital goods are non-refundable.</p>

            <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
              <div>
                <a
                  href={cta_url}
                  target="_blank"
                  class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 rounded-md font-semibold text-white bg-book-theme hover:bg-book-hover focus:outline-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
                >
                  Get It Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-4 lg:flex lg:items-center"
        >
          <a class="book-container" href={cta_url}>
            <div class="book">
              <Image
                src="/BookOfWisdom.png"
                width={300}
                height={600}
                alt="The Book of Wisdom PDF Cover"
                format="avif"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
